name: Nanak Industries
overview: Established in the year 2006, we, “Nanak Industries”, are one of the leading organizations, engaged in manufacturing and supplying a comprehensive range of Precision Engineering Parts. Under this range, we provide Industrial Bolt, Carriage Bolt, J Bolt, L Bolt, U Bolt, P Bolt, Industrial Rod, Stud, Pin and Rivet to our clients. All our products are designed and developed using high-grade raw material and latest machinery that are obtained from the reliable vendors of the market to ensure that these meet with good quality standard. These products are widely appreciated by the customers for their corrosion & abrasion resistance, zero maintenance, easy fitting, longer functional life, dimensional accuracy and compact designs.
